snippet.title: Toad vs. Wart || Reveal Trailer!
snippet.description:
Before jumping in the Shroom Shines Escapade... 
...TOAD shall save the day from Wart's villanous intents!!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Toad vs. Wart" is a "Mario vs. Donkey Kong" inspired Super Mario Bros X2 mini-episode! 
To stop Wart, you'll need to travel through many small levels, solve puzzles, collect Star Coins, defeat enemies, and find your way out!... Basically : Find the Key and keep goin'!

Releases in 2024!
